- Use the `vscode` namespace for all VS Code API interactions
- Implement proper error handling and logging
- Utilize `vscode.commands.registerCommand` for command registration
- Follow the VS Code extension guidelines for activation events
- Ensure compatibility with different VS Code versions using `engines`